edu.memphis.ccrg.lida.framework.initialization
Class LidaFactoriesXMLLoader

java.lang.Object
  edu.memphis.ccrg.lida.framework.initialization.LidaFactoriesXMLLoader

public class LidaFactoriesXMLLoader
extends java.lang.Object

Loads the factoriesData.xml file which configures the factories of the framework i.e. what strategies are used by the objects created by the factory, the types of node, links, and codelets that can be created as well.

Author:
Javier Snaider
